data.description: This house is too cute to pass up, completely updated 3/2 on a great lot in Camino. Just minutes away from the freeway but in a great neighborhood with the best sledding spot in the winter! The main floor has a super cute Kitchen with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances open floorplan to  2 good sized bedrooms with views, full bathroom, wood stove and street entrance from your oversized covered patio/carport. The lower level has another large bedroom with an full 2nd bathroom, laundry room with freezer space, 2nd family room and outside access, this space could also easily be turned into a apartment for income potential with its own access.  New HVAC installed summer 2023 and new 10x10 tuff shed installed in 2021. Don't miss out on this turn key home today, its got space for all!! Extra cars? no problem? Dogs? no biggie! Check it out!
